Class GridSquare

  • java.lang.Object

      • java.awt.Container

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
    public class GridSquare
extends javax.swing.JComponent
    Types 0 -> Blank display square 1 -> Display Square displaying summation 2 -> Input square
    Author:
    Antoine Farley GridSquare that makes up a puzzle. Contains a Display square if grid needs to show sums or is blank or contains an input square if square is meant to accept user input
